videos.description: Terence Davis finishes in transition with a reverse lay-in.
videos.headline: Ole Miss' Davis hits reverse layup

videos.description: Marcanvis Hymon gets two technical fouls four minutes into the game and taunts the Kentucky crowd waving his arms as he leaves the court.
videos.headline: Rebels' Hymon is ejected four minutes into the game

videos.description: Shai Gilgeous-Alexanderin goes transitions and into the paint for a layup.
videos.headline: Gilgeous-Alexander blows by defenders for lay-in

videos.description: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander chucks it down the court to Kevin Knox who takes it to the rim for a dunk.
videos.headline: Wildcats' Knox slams one home on leak-out

videos.description: Bruce Stevens sets up a screen and later makes a wide-open 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Ole Miss' Stevens swishes in triple

videos.description: Breein Tyree shows no mercy to the rim, dunking over Wenyen Gabriel who gets a technical for shoving Tyree right after the play.
videos.headline: Rebels' Tyree dunks hard on Gabriel

videos.description: Kevin Knox misses a three-point shot, but PJ Washington slams home the board.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Washington slams in rebound

videos.description: The Wildcats have five players in double digits and improve to 10-7 in the conference.
videos.headline: No. 23 Kentucky rolls past Ole Miss 96-78

tracking.trackingName: SEC_NCB Highlight (No 23 Kentucky beats Ole Miss) 180228 ESHEET

videos.description: Things get scrappy in the beginning of the game, but in the end Kentucky pulls away with the win 96-78.
videos.headline: Kentucky dominates against Ole Miss
